snippet.title: Barkley Gaiden²: The Son Of Dark Draker: Barkley Shut Up and Jam: Gaiden, Gaiden Episode 1
snippet.description:
Play it now!  https://tunicate.itch.io/barkley

Not the usual Deltarune content, but check out Barkley Gaiden²: The Son Of Dark Draker: Barkley Shut Up and Jam: Gaiden, Gaiden Episode 1!  This project has been in the works for a few years and I helped!

Barkley: Shut Up and Jam! Gaiden is a classic indie RPG from 2008.  Its much-anticipated sequel had a successful kickstarter but development ran into issues and the game was never completed.  But today, 11/11/23, the promise has been fulfilled.  Barkley:Gaiden:Gaiden Episode 1 is a fan game which begins the conclusion of the epic Hoopz Barkley SaGa.
